<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>가입 완료</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #f8f8f8;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', 'Apple SD Gothic Neo', Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .success-container {
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 48px 32px 40px 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .success-check {
      font-size: 56px;
      color: #267C13;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      display: inline-block;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .success-title {
      color: #267C13;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .success-welcome {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .success-desc {
      color: #444;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .success-btn {
      background: #267C13;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 14px 0;
      width: 100%;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .success-btn:hover {
      background: #1b570e;
    }

    @media (max-width: 500px) {
      .success-container {
        padding: 24px 8px;
        max-width: 98vw;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="success-container">
    <div class="success-check">✔</div>
    <div class="success-title">가입 완료</div>
    <div class="success-welcome">환영합니다!</div>
    <div class="success-desc">로그인하여 당신의 정원에서 첫 씨앗을 심어보세요!</div>
    <a href="/login" class="success-btn">로그인하러 가기</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

